1. About
========

This is a complete set of modulair services for ircu u2.10.11.07+asuka(1.2.1)
and u2.10.12.10+snircd(1.3.0).
So far it includes:
N: Services Core: it can load/unload and rehash the modules.

  1.1. Modules
  ------------

      Q: Channel & Oper Service: It has all functions needed for user to
         authenticate and manage their channels. It also has an extensive
         set of oper commands.
      S: Spamscan: It will scan channels for spam & advertising and will take 
         appropriate action against malicious persons.
      R: Request Service: It can be used to request L (QuakeNet Dev-Com
         https://svn.quakenet.org/svn/quakenet/lightweight/ ),
         Q and S.
      G: Help Service: It can issue tickets for help channels, and has a queue
         system.
      U: Game Service: It has a few games built in and can be easely expanded.
  Tutor: Tutorial Service: can give automated tutorials to a channel.
      V: vHost service (only compatible with snircd, DISABLE on asuka).

